Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子死了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The kid die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死在了人行道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On the pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫杰夫·邓肯  没有前科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His name is Jeff Duncan. Zero priors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在腰带上持有一把合法枪支\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Had a legal gun in his waistband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为超速被喊停车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pulled over for going seven over the speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠特尼·杨高中毕业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Graduate of Whitney Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前在芝加哥大学就读\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Student at University of Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警员呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪的培训官  叫戴维·韦兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The FTO who fired the shot, Dave Wheelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边的警员刚警校毕业一个月  叫安德烈·库珀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}PPO a month out of the academy is named Andre Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库珀说了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cooper's talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟事件响应小组和民警问责办公室都说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh yeah, to IRT and COPA,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的证词从未改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and his statement never changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰夫压根就没有去掏枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeff never went for his weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有理由去使用致命手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was zero justification to use deadly force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有三名目击证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I also have three witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外加两个警用监控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and two POD cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内务部正在去韦兰警官家的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}IAD is on their way to Officer Wheelan's house now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望找两名便衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I would like two undercovers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮助押送他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to make the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...  那不是我团队的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's... That's not what my unit does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说想找个芝加哥警官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean I think you'd be hard pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意掺和到这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to find any Chicago police officer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-恐怕很难  -我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- who wants to step in this. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白过去的经验告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know history tells us that this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事是不能介入的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is not something to step in,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才找我信任的团队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which is why I'm asking a unit I trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望他们能信任我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I hope trusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个视频我看了有三十多遍  汉克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've watched this footage three dozen times, Hank,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,州检察官也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as has the SA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事已经很清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it's as clear as this moment ever comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不良用枪行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was a bad shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能找两名警官吗  博伊特警长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you spare two officers, Sergeant Voight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视频还没有在网上疯传\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The video's not yet viral,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们会让所有警官立即进入12小时工作状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we will be putting every officer on immediate 12s.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们预计会有大量示威和暴力情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We expect mass protests and violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我们要行动迅速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we will move fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特沃特警官  鲁塞克警官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Officer Atwater, Officer Ruzek,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求你们前往韦兰警官的家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to go to Officer Wheelan's home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以杀人罪逮捕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and arrest him for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}芝加哥警署\N第八季  第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴维·韦兰警官  从警三十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Officer Dave Wheelan, on the job 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16次局内表彰  一年只有1次投诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}16 department commendations, only one complaint a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么念他的事都行  但听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can read about him all you want, but listen to me:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是代步车  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're both nothing more than an Uber, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣读他的权利  逮捕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Read him his rights, arrest him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车载上他  把他放到南区拘留所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}drive him, drop him off at south detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么都不用做  什么都不要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You do nothing, you say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要掺和进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do not get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你们作证时惹麻烦的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not one word that can get you in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个字都不要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you have to testify,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听明白了吗  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- you understand me? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  车已经准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, car's been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有警察标记的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's unmarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是别的部门来干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Should be another unit doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得任何好警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like any good cop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都应该能去逮捕这种警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}should be able to arrest a cop like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉这个档案太少了  不可能是全部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean this file's real sparse. This can't be the whole of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他弄得像是个在常规停车检查时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It makes him look like a good cop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死个孩子的好警察似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who murdered a kid at a routine traffic stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常规是没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, routine all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他家里没有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't have guns in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有个妻子和孩子  她们会很激动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got a wife and kids. They're gonna be all emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-琳内特  -二位好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, Linette. - Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-想象一下杰夫·邓肯的家人吧  -我想过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Imagine Jeff Duncan's family. - I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我们不是去杰夫·邓肯家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only we're not going to Jeff Duncan's house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-去抓人的  -谢谢  琳内特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- to arrest nobody. - Thank you, Linette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着兄弟  我理解这个情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, brother, I know that this is a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会让我们面对很多种不同情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that can spin us in a lot of different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分情况都不在我们的能力范围内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of those ways are above our pay grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此就像博伊特说的  这事与我们无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So like Voight said, this got nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就去像抓罪犯那样逮捕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's just go arrest this guy like the criminal he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不节外生枝  回来该干嘛干嘛  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nice and easy, get back to doing our real jobs, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕的事显然是走漏风声了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the arrest clearly leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们知道我们要来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Knew we were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的搭档在里面  我只是想和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My partner's in there. I just wanna talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是韦兰的培训生吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that Wheelan's trainee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, man. You're not gonna touch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要命令我走开  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you're not gonna tell me to walk away, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有权来这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have every right to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该被强制休假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He should be on mandatory leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯文  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Kev. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  都没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right. Hey, we all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道他为什么对他开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, I just need to know why he shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们私下聊聊好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can we have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  库珀  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, man. Cooper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对  -阿特沃特  鲁塞克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Atwater, Ruzek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没进去过吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ain't been in there, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我明白我不应该进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I haven't. I get that I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我当时就在场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, yeah, man, I was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就站在他身旁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was right there next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那哥们一起巡视一个月了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I rode with that dude a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟  我就是需要明白这是为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Brother, I just need to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你知道你应该回家去  离开这吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you know you gotta go home. Get out of here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  有我们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay, we got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  我们几分钟后就回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. We'll be back in a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别耽搁太久啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦兰太太吗  我是鲁塞克警官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Wheelan, I'm Officer Ruzek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是阿特沃特警官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Officer Atwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天  进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
