Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to step out of the vehicle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被捕了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I being arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你下令了  下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just gave an order. Step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你上司来  我不下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call your supervisor. I'm not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么用枪指着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why the hell is a gun pointed at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Step out of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦兰  长官  我们冷静下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wheelan, sir, let's just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  韦兰  冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Wheelan. Calm down.
