Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  这是入侵式搜查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, that's an intrusive search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  搜车  否则就等着被开吧  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kid, do it or find a new job, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  转过身去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hands up! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿枪指着我  而我什么都没做错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your gun is pointed at me, and I did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我拒绝  -我说最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- So no. - Last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  远离武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get your hands up, away from the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后转过身去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韦兰  你别激动  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, hey, Wheelan. Let's just relax, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不动  我知道我的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not moving. I know my rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打电话给你上级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call your supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去  把手从武器上拿开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn around. Hands away from the weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手根本没靠近武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My hands are nowhere near my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们冷静下  -转过身去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Let's just calm down. - Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不动  你开枪打我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ain't gonna move so you can shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冷静下  韦兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's just calm down. Wheelan--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这下看到了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不听从命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wouldn't comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有敌意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He--he was hostile,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他携带武器  他还动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was armed, and he moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心自己的生命安全  就采取了行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feared for my life, and I acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想告诉我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean to tell me all--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海莉没说给我们增援吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hailey didn't say we were getting backup, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get down!
