Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头  跟着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get your head down. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头  低头  过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep your head down. Head down, come on.
