Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-凯文你掩护我  -我掩护我掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Kev got me, you got me? - I got it, I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们在屋里  鲁塞克  -上车  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- They're in the house, Ruz.. - Get in the truck, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走  快走  快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go, let's go, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了吗  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You got it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-狗娘养的  -该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Son of a bitch. - Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫指挥中心  有人开枪袭警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}10-1, 10-1! Shots fired at the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got another shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们安全了吗  我们安全了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are we clear? Tell me we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  没人跟来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, yeah. No tail, no follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打中其中一个了  至少有两名杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I shot one of them. There's at least two shooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手铐打开  打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take these cuffs off. Take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是警察  跟你们一样  -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm a cop, same as you! - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天啊  -你们听得到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- God. - Tell me you got your ears on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-警长  我们的人遭到了伏击  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sarge, our guys got ambushed. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧  我在无线电上听到了整件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you okay? I heard the whole thing over the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  有人袭击了安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, somebody hit the safehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是什么意思  袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell does he mean, hit?
