Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打中了其中一个杀手  或者两个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We hit one of the shooters, maybe two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都带着面具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Both were masked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方的信息显然被泄露了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, the place was clearly compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是去那里杀韦兰的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were there to kill Wheelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当  你们还在安全屋吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Adam, are you still at the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  我们离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no, we're driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡逻队说他们一分钟就到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Patrol said they were a minute out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在离开感觉更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but driving feels safer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在到安全屋去  看看是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, we are heading to the safe house now, see what we can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到地方停车  等我们派人保护你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Find a location off road, hang tight until we get you an escort,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用无线电设备通讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and use only your DCs to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  鲁塞克  车库  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yo, Ruz. Garage. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没受伤  把手铐打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wasn't hit. Take the cuffs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-转过去  -我没受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Turn around. - I'm not hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能把我带去另外一个安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you know you can't take me to another safehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们在第一个安全屋找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause if they found us at the first one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能找到下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they're gonna find us at the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在追杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're hunting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在到底怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情很不对头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's something very wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些枪手找到了安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those shooters just made a safehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我们现在要问问自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know. What we gotta do is ask ourselves this question:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有内鬼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was it an inside job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有芝加哥警署的人知道安全屋的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only people that know about the safehouse is CPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用说他们比巡逻队早两分钟到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not to mention, they just beat patrol by two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想现在最安全的做法就是我们保密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think the safest thing is we keep this between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密地带他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we take him off book,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到没人知道的地方去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we take him somewhere nobody knows about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我们搞清楚到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}till we can figure out what the hell's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁在追杀他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who the hell's hunting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密地带他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take him off book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密地带他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take him off book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大  我们有个计划  不用护卫队了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boss, we got a plan. Disregard that escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are we looking at?
