Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们刚把他照片打印出来  不过我们运气好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They just printed him, but I'm thinking we're gonna get a pop.
