Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹壳是.32口径的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's .32 caliber shell casings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边一路过来都是9毫米口径的子弹壳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Got 9 mil casings all the way over here.
