Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们不担心交火  破釜沉舟的亡命之徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they didn't care about crossfire. This is a do or die crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-看来不是十几岁的菜鸟  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We're probably not looking at teenage foot soldiers. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米勒什么时候到的这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when did Miller get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比我们先到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She got here before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你过来看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, can I show you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟们  给我们点空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guys, give us the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有手下的消息了  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You heard from your guys? - I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们没事吧  -没受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Well, they all right? - No injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们现在在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在秘密转移韦兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're transporting Wheelan off book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话关机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They turned their cells off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟你一起做的决定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And they made that call with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They did. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果韦兰或者任何平民有一丝可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My men are not gonna bring Wheelan in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在路上挨枪子儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if there is any chance that he or any civilian
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手下都不会把他带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}could take a bullet while en route, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是想就我们刚刚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need to try and give me an order
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏入的政治丑闻而下令  请便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause of the political dirt we just stepped in, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到这里来是因为我拉你入了泥潭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here because I had you step in the dirt with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会给你任何命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not giving you any orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你们怎么决定  都是最终决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever your call is, that's the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派人去调查芝加哥警署可能存在的泄密人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got a team digging into a potential leak at CPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信我  汉克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You trusted me, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你现在得把我的手铐打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, you need to take my cuffs off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会帮你打开手铐  别再说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody's taking them off. Stop asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能坐以待毙  像畜生一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not gonna be a defenseless animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-坐下  -我不是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sit down. - I'm not the criminal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗  那谁是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No? Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打死的那个19岁的黑人小孩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The 19-year-old Black kid you shot down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I defended myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防一个大学生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From a college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有权自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had the right to defend my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自卫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯文  别争了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kev. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  自卫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚看了视频  你让我看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just watched the video. You told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了一个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You murdered a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要站在我面前  大言不惭地说你是自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you're gonna stand here in front of me and defend yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别管了  -别管了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just let it go. - Let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也站在你面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's standing in front of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我们可能要在这待上一阵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I'm saying is, we might be here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些争吵都帮不上忙  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}None of this is helping. That's all I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了  他不值得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let it go. He's not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的手铐打开  你知道我是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uncuff me. You know I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先跟你把话说清楚  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanna make something really clear to you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带你来这的唯一原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only reason we brought you here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保护你不被暗杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was to keep you from being assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不意味着我们有人认为你是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't mean either of us think that you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁塞克和阿特沃特不能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruzek and Atwater can't move
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我们确认泄密的人不是自己人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until we determine that leak wasn't inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并抓到第二个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we got that second shooter in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以谁想要戴维·韦兰警官的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So who the hell is going after Officer Dave Wheelan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机技术人员刚把死掉抢手的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, mobile techs just sent over the fingerprint card
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指纹卡送来  雷·麦克斯  25岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on our dead shooter. Ray Macks, 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮派组证实他是死神帮的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gangs has him hooked up with the Rollin' Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的老大  TJ·琼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His boss, T-J Jones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好是杰夫·邓肯的继弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just so happens to be the half-brother of Jeff Duncan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TJ的帮派都是职业杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}T-J runs a crew of hired guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把自己视为"帮派警察"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They think of themselves as the "police of gangland."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以TJ的继弟被一个警察杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So T-J's half-brother gets killed by a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他派了两个手下去杀那个警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he sends two of his guys to kill that police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保持着街头秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's keeping order on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有TJ的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got anything on T-J?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没有公开逮捕令  没有假释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no open warrants, no longer on probation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很怀疑他是否有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I seriously doubt he's carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮派组已经盯上他有一阵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, Gangs has been on it for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没找到任何能逮捕他的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they have nothing to arrest him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但他肯定认识第二个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, he knows our second shooter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何我们要让他跟我们开口谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we're gonna make him talk to us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰  你和我走  拿上卷宗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jay, you and me. Grab that file.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是来找TJ的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're just here to talk to T-J.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TJ\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}T-j.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们会来  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're expecting us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟被你们的人杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My brother was murdered by your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们是为了这件事而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd hope you'd come for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是你来的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if that is why you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想让你去警局和我们谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We want you to come in and talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有目击者  我不和警察谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't talk to police without a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  在这里有这么一大帮人盯着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen, talking out here with all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会同意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just not gonna work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我猜我们别谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then I guess we won't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有可以逮捕我的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have anything to arrest me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  确实没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你朋友汤姆吧  汤姆·格雷根  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this your friend, Tom? You Tom Greggin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也叫格雷格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}AKA Gregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚假释两个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're two months into probation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沃尔特·卡尔明  六个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's Walter Culmin. Six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又是谁  那是吉米·马基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who we got out here? That's Jimmy Markey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉塞尔·沃尔  你跟两个孩子一起生活  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Russell Wall, you got your two kids living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还知道这是乔·哈特  他妈靠他生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I know this is Joe Hart, who's got his mom living on his dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能继续说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但显然你喜欢和重罪犯人交好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's pretty clear you're all fraternizing with felons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假释官已经在路上了  除非我们让他们别来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've got parole officers on their way unless we call them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如你来警局和我们谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you say you come in and talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不用毁了所有人的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we don't have to keep ruining everyone's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被捕了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I under arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还是把我的律师叫来  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Call my lawyer anyway. - Yeah, got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着拍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷和另外一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ray and a second man
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要杀死一个囚犯和两个警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tried to kill a prisoner and two cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷现在死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ray is dead now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个人逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the second guy got away.
