Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两小时前你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where were you two hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在图享上跟我女友视频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Live on the Gram with my girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们早就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自愿把手机给你们了  你们问我要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I willingly gave you my phone. You asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你和女友打电话时一定不好受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I imagine that call with your lady friend must've been rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样失去了你的继弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, losing your half-brother like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又死了一个黑人  被警察击毙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}another Black man gone, shot by a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TJ  那个警察要面临谋杀指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}T-J, that cop was being brought in on murder charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗  谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You understand? Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝加哥警署一定会严办这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}CPD is doing this one right.
