Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再把杰夫称为我的继弟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is if you wouldn't call Jeff my half-brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是我弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的血肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们关系很好  我们理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys were close. We understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但枪击警察  TJ\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But shooting at the cops, T-J?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伸张正义  就算是我们警察也得信任系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To get justice, even us cops have to trust the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的唯一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's what we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的唯一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的系统不保护你的社区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our system doesn't protect your neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你保护  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:23:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但信任系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But trust the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意花五十万信任系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You willing to bet half a billion on that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是给警察渎职买单吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}instead of paying police misconduct bills?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得如果你们好好看看自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think if you both looked at yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会得出同样的结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'd know the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在我们的社区蹲点并不是为了保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Y'all ain't in my neighborhood camped out to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那只是为了确保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Y'all only there to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些人不流窜到城市的其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we don't leak out into the rest of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.09,0:24:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没枪击谁  我从不开枪打人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I shot no one. I never shot anyone.
