Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有我的任何证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have nothing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I'd like to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.73,0:24:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的不在场证明很完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His alibi's rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.06,0:24:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝对不是第二个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's definitely not our second shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.37,0:24:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的律师来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, did his lawyer show yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.78,0:24:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了  他已经威胁要起诉我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, he's already threatening to sue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.13,0:24:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我们非法带TJ来警局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says we brought T-J in unlawfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.80,0:24:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要求我们立即释放他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he wants a release right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.97,0:25:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那TJ的手机呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about T-J's phone?
