Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.49,0:25:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙很聪明  但组织犯罪技术部正在查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The guy's really smart, but our OCD techs are on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就放了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So we'll release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.40,0:25:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在他车上放个追踪器  让战术小队待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just get a tracker on his car and put a tac team on it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要动用所有资源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're gonna take everything we got
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并彻底核查TJ手机上的内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and put it up against everything in T-J's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.83,0:25:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  第二个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Believe me, that second shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.79,0:25:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就躲在那其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is gonna be buried in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.88,0:25:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.35,0:25:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  雷·麦克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, Ray Macks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他是其中一个枪手  你认识他吗  -不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He's one of the shooters. You recognize him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.50,0:25:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那好  TJ·琼斯  -不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right, T-J Jones. - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.67,0:25:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恩格尔伍德待了三十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've been in Englewood 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.34,0:25:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你从没见过这些面孔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you're going to tell me you've never seen those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我见过好多次这些面孔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, I've seen those faces a bunch of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.84,0:25:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行  这算是个开头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, that's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.44,0:25:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉我他们帮派里还有谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You tell us who's in their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.13,0:25:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是说我见过那些表情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I mean I've seen those faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些"我恨警察"的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The "I hate cops" faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.41,0:25:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恩格尔伍德和谁有私人恩怨吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have any personal beefs in Englewood?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.56,0:25:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  帮帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, man. Help us out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.68,0:25:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我们都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, yeah, we all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我工作的地方  就是警察对抗其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where I work, it's us versus them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一出现  他们就觉得是侵占军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We show up, they see an occupying force.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nah, not all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.02,0:25:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:26:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  每次我们出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, every time we show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.24,0:26:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有了剑拔弩张的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we starting a bad relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.50,0:26:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.58,0:26:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是穿着警察制服  带着警徽和枪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're the city's secret thoughts and fears
