Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我爸以前也爱说这种屁话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, my dad used to say the same stupid thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.21,0:26:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我们抓到第二个枪手  否则我们不能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We cannot leave here until we get this other shooter in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.36,0:26:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我知道  -那帮帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I know that. - Then help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.27,0:26:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在帮你们  但我不知道名字  懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am helping you out, but I don't have any names, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.88,0:26:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就向我开枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're just shooting at me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.07,0:26:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我在尽我的职责  你懂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I was doing my job, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.54,0:26:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的职责  是吗  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Your job, huh? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是吗  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.27,0:26:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说说你的职责是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Explain your job to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.59,0:26:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不想死  -别说这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, I didn't wanna die. - There's no talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所以我...  -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- So I did-- - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.38,0:26:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.39,0:26:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米勒办公室刚确认泄密人不在警局内部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Miller's office just confirmed the leak was not from inside CPD,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.09,0:26:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个枪手查的怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so where are we at with that second shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.71,0:26:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快查到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织犯罪技术部调出了TJ手机里的所有号码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}OCD tech pulled all the numbers from T-J's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.74,0:26:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有11个也在死去枪手的手机上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only 11 of those were also on the dead shooter's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.53,0:26:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中五个  包括死去抢手的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Five of those, including the dead shooter's,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在三个月前一起购买并激活的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}were purchased and activated together three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.05,0:26:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们猜是TJ买的  -好  懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We're guessing T-J got them first. - Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.70,0:26:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个号码的所有信号位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only one number pinged to every tower
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:27:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟死去抢手的手机一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}alongside the dead shooter's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.14,0:27:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是第二个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This has gotta be our guy right here.
