Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.21,0:28:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我只是说说  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I'm just saying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保护了这些人三十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three decades I protected those people,
