Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.60,0:29:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为白人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Being white.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.49,0:29:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为白人  真的假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Being white? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是黑人也能分辨黑白对错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't gotta be Black to know wrong from right.
