Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.86,0:29:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到我说了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you hear me say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.91,0:29:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想这个白人做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think about what this white man did
