Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下一个黑人小孩会怎么看你  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- the next time you go out there. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.19,0:29:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但我现在不和你争论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know, but I'm not doing this with you right now.
