Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.58,0:30:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不是  我不是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because I don't! That's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.50,0:30:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他内心的丑恶不代表我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's inside of him is not inside of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.45,0:30:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你最应该明白这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you should be the one to know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.60,0:30:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么敢说这样的话  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How dare you, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了你一天到晚质疑我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sick of you questioning me all the time.
