Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.23,0:30:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  你瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道我是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He knows I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.36,0:30:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的老爸也会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and your old man would say the same thing.
