Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.99,0:30:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我担心自己有生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, yeah. I feared for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.63,0:30:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没有生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your life wasn't even in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.33,0:30:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你觉得事发时我感觉不出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you don't think I can feel when it is?
