Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.59,0:31:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉不出来吗  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when my life is danger? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.27,0:31:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为自己有生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feared for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.88,0:31:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕杰夫·邓肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You feared Jeff Duncan.
