Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.68,0:31:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.47,0:31:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我看到了一个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I saw a man who lost empathy
