Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.54,0:31:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他拒绝...  -我看到一个心惊胆战的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He resisted-- - I saw a man who was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.51,0:31:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他...  -害怕那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He was-- - Scared of those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.93,0:31:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你在开枪之前就已经害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you were scared way before you even pulled the trigger.
